ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[So far both the confirmed cases (both of whom have died) and the 4
suspected cases (all still alive) of Marburg hemorrhagic fever in
Luanda, the capital city of Angola, have originated in the northern
province of Uige where the outbreak is centered, and there has been
no transmission of infection locally in the capital city. - Mod.CP]
